パッケージ com.worksap.nlp.sudachi

  • インタフェースのサマリー 
    インタフェース 説明
    Dictionary
    A lexicon and a grammar for morphological analysis.
    InputText<E>
    An immutable sequence of characters.
    InputTextBuilder<E>
    A mutable sequence of characters.
    Lattice
    A graph structure used in the morphological analysis.
    LatticeNode
    A node of Lattice.
    Morpheme
    A morpheme.
    Tokenizer
    A tokenizer of morphological analysis.
  • クラスのサマリー 
    クラス 説明
    DictionaryFactory
    Build a Dictionary instance from a dictionary file.
    EditConnectionCostPlugin
    A plugin for editing the connection costs.
    InputTextPlugin
    A plugin that rewrites the characters of input texts.
    LatticeNodeImpl  
    MorphemeList  
    OovProviderPlugin
    A plugin that provides the nodes of out-of-vocabulary morphemes.
    PathRewritePlugin
    A plugin that rewrite the best path of the lattice.
    Settings
    A structure of settings.
    SudachiCommandLine
    A command-line morphological analysis tool.

    列挙型 説明
